(75, 1, '2017-07-05 06:02:58', '2017-07-05 06:02:58', 'ViewFin™ is a market leader in Blockchain technology and the developer of Metaverse™, the first public Blockchain in China. As the most visionary Fintech company in China, ViewFin™ has assembled together a team of domestic and international specialists from various industries such as the financial, internet, consulting and Blockchain industries to implement future Fintech applications.', 'viewfin blog', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'viewfinblog', '', '', '2017-07-05 09:28:50', '2017-07-05 09:28:50', '', 19, 'http://192.168.1.35/?page_id=75', 0, 'page', '', 0),
